name: Super InVRaders Turbo | Early Access
summary: Get ready to experience a new level of fitness with our virtual reality game! In this game, you will face off against invaders who are threatening to destroy the earth. But don't worry, you won't just be fighting them with your strength - you'll also need to hit in the rhythm to land your attacks! Get your heart pumping and your muscles moving as you take on wave after wave of enemies, all while saving the planet. It's time to show off your fitness skills and become the hero the world needs!
